abstract: >-
  Reproducible Python workflow for archive auditing, waveform derivation,
  action-specific constrained REML, whole-athlete cluster bootstrap,
  sensitivity analysis, participant-code and exact-deduplication robustness,
  alternative functional aggregation, and publication-figure generation for
  a secondary analysis of the TTMD6 motion-capture archive.
